article_title: Michael Sam likely heading to Dallas Cowboys’ practice squad
article_text:
Topics: michael sam, NFL, Entertainment News, Politics News

The Dallas Cowboys are set to sign Michael Sam onto the team’s practice squad, according to a report from NFL Insider’s Ian Rapoport and multiple other sources.

A team source said that if Sam passes his physical, he’ll be added to the practice squad. So while Sam may not be making history with the Rams, he could very well be making history with the Cowboys.

More to come.

article_metadata.description: The team has brought Sam in for a physical and appears set to bring him on board
